---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '@components/layout/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import SchemaMarkup from '@components/seo/SchemaMarkup.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About IGET Vapes Original | Australia"
  description="Learn about IGET Vapes Original, our adult retail standards, authentic product focus, and Australia-wide delivery support."
>
  <SchemaMarkup type="organization" />
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ name: 'About Us' }]} />

  <div class="max-w-4xl">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>About IGET Vapes Original</h1>
      <p>A sharper, more deliberate adult retail experience built around genuine IGET and Alibarbar products, clear service expectations, and Australia-wide delivery.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>
        <strong>IGET Vapes Original</strong> is designed for adults who want a cleaner way to buy genuine vape products online. Instead of a crowded marketplace feel, the store is built around curation, clarity, and confidence: authentic stock, clear checkout rules, and a calmer path from browsing to order confirmation.
      </p>

      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        We focus on genuine <strong>IGET</strong> and <strong>Alibarbar</strong> ranges because that is where product confidence, flavour variety, and repeat-order value are strongest for our customers. The goal is simple: make adult purchasing decisions easier without leaning on low-trust design patterns or generic discount-store language.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every device listed on the site is sourced through authorised supply. We do not treat authenticity like a footnote. It is central to the brand, the checkout flow, and the way the store communicates with customers.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Product Range</h2>
      <p>The catalogue is organised by use-case, not just by brand name. That means adults can move quickly between long-session devices, compact value options, and refillable pod systems:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/jnr-cruiser">JNR Cruiser 12000</a></strong> for high-capacity, rechargeable performance and bold all-day flavour.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/iget-one">IGET One 12000</a></strong> for adults who want stronger vapour density in a sleeker form factor.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/iget-bar-pro">IGET Bar Pro 10000</a></strong> for broad flavour choice and dependable everyday value.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/iget-bar-plus-s3">IGET Bar Plus S3</a></strong> for reusable hardware and smarter long-term spend.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/iget-bar-plus-s3-pod">S3 replacement pods</a></strong> for lower-cost flavour rotation after the initial kit purchase.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/alibarbar-ingot">Alibarbar Ingot 9000</a></strong> for compact value with a rich flavour-first profile.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/alibarbar-ice-adjust">Alibarbar Ice Adjust 12000</a></strong> for adults who want adjustable cooling intensity.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why Adults Choose Us</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 not-prose mb-6">
        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-text mb-2">100% Genuine Products</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Every listed product comes through authorised supply. Authenticity is treated like a core product promise, not a footer claim.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-text mb-2">Structured Product Discovery</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Ranges are framed by value, puff count, and use-case so customers can compare faster and choose with less hesitation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-text mb-2">Clear Shipping Expectations</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Australia-wide delivery, discreet packaging, and state-based shipping rates are made clear before the final checkout step.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-text mb-2">Bundle-Led Value</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Pricing stays competitive, but the bigger unlock is in <a href="/mix-and-match" class="text-accent hover:underline">Mix &amp; Match deals</a> and S3 refill economics for repeat buyers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>
        The commitment is straightforward: present adult vape products with more rigour, better taste, and fewer trust gaps than the average category site. That means a real age gate, visible checkout thresholds, and a design system that feels considered from first click to order confirmation.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you are comparing the latest <strong>IGET Bar Pro</strong>, exploring <strong>Alibarbar</strong>, or building a refillable S3 setup, the store is designed to help you move with confidence rather than guesswork.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        If you need help with an order, delivery timing, payment instructions, or the right range for your needs, head to our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>. For checkout details, you can also review the <a href="/shipping-policy">Shipping Policy</a>, <a href="/payment-methods">Payment Methods</a>, and <a href="/delivery">Delivery Locations</a> pages.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
